ms until the Coruscating Mines were itemized. Now we have at least two +2 envenom items and lots more +stealth. Short end of the stick? I think so. Who wants to wade through 36 levels or more to get envenom any spec bonuses aside from stealth, piercing, and blades.<br>
<br>
Please note that the observations above are from my experiences in game. I haven't looked at any sites that catelog items so there possibly could be some out there. I've just never seen them.<br>
<br>
On a side note I think they did a terrible job with the 40th epic rewards. I was thinking about the +spec on the weapons and my Druid buddy who got one. That bonus is totaly wasted on him. Kind of silly to do an epic quest, supposedly for your class, and get something where half the bonuses are wasted. <p><table width="600" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
