<br>
<br>
Twisted Darksteel Ring +2 CS, also gives ~4 to dex and quickness<br>
<br>
Moonshadow Cloak(epic) +1 CS, gives dex and qui as well<br>
<br>
Braided Darksteel Gloves 82Af, 1 step down from the 92af Webbed Shadow.  gives +1 CS<br>
<br>
Possibly a very very rare drop gloves that comes from werewolves that give +1 CS, only 88af, but might be 100% qual, making them pretty close to end game.<br>
<br>
<br>
Heres a quick rundown of stealth items too, in case you're interested.<br>
<br>
____Steel necklace(i cant remember if its darksteel, silksteel, or shadowsteel) +2 stealth, but also +2 battlesongs,a nd a few con/str, so pretty sought after by skalds as well<br>
<br>
Webbed Shadow Helm 92af +4 Stealth<br>
Moonshadow Cloak(epic) +1 Stealth<br>
Braided Darksteel Boots 82af +2? Stealth<br>
Ghostly Cloak +4 stealth +4 battlesongs lvl 44+ item i think.<br>
<br>
I'm missing one there somewhere, because I'm at +8 or 9 stealth at least, and I don't have the Necklace nor Ghostly cloak yet.  I'll edit with exact stats of this stuff soon.<br>
